    All Classes and Interfaces

    Class
    Description
    AddTagsRequest
    Data Transfer Object (DTO) used for adding one or more tags to an eatery.
    AdminActionLog
    Entity representing an administrative action log entry.
    AdminActionLogRepository
    Repository interface for performing CRUD and custom queries on AdminActionLog entities.
    AdminDashboardController
    Controller that provides REST endpoints for the admin dashboard.
    AdminLogController
    Controller that manages access to administrative action logs.
    AdminReviewModerationController
    Controller responsible for administrative review moderation actions.
    AggregatedRatingsResponse
    Data Transfer Object (DTO) representing aggregated review statistics for an eatery.
    AuthResponse
    Data Transfer Object (DTO) representing the response returned after a successful authentication (login or signup) operation.
    AuthService
    Service layer handling authentication and user account management logic for the HealthyAura application.
    CorsConfig
    Configuration class for handling Cross-Origin Resource Sharing (CORS) settings in the application.
    CrowdController
    Controller responsible for providing crowd level information for eateries.
    CrowdDisplayDTO
    Data Transfer Object (DTO) representing the crowd level display information for a specific eatery.
    CrowdService
    Service class responsible for estimating and displaying real-time crowd levels for eateries within the HealthyAura application.
    DatabaseSeeder
    Configuration class responsible for seeding initial data into the database upon application startup.
    DietaryTags
    Entity representing a dietary tag associated with an Eatery.
    DietaryTagsRepository
    Repository interface for performing CRUD and query operations on DietaryTags entities.
    Eatery
    Entity representing a healthier eatery registered in the HealthyAura database.
    EateryController
    Controller responsible for managing eatery-related operations.
    EateryRepository
    Repository interface for performing CRUD and custom query operations on Eatery entities.
    EateryRequest
    Data Transfer Object (DTO) used for handling eatery creation, update, and retrieval requests between the backend and frontend.
    EateryService
    Service layer responsible for handling all eatery-related operations such as fetching, saving, searching, and tagging.
    GlobalExceptionHandler
    Global exception handler for all controllers in the HealthyAura application.

    homeController
    Controller that handles homepage content and personalized or general recommendations for users.
    JwtAuthenticationFilter
    Security filter responsible for validating JSON Web Tokens (JWT) in incoming HTTP requests before they reach the controller layer.
    JwtUtil
    Utility class responsible for generating, validating, and parsing JSON Web Tokens (JWT) used in the HealthyAura authentication system.
    loginController
    Controller responsible for user authentication and account creation.
    LoginRequest
    Data Transfer Object (DTO) representing a login request payload.
    Points
    Entity representing a user's reward points balance within the HealthyAura system.
    PointsRepository
    Repository interface for performing CRUD and custom query operations on Points entities.
    PointsResponse
    Data Transfer Object (DTO) representing a user's reward points summary.
    ProfileController
    Controller responsible for managing user profile operations such as retrieving profile details, updating preferences, and modifying account information.
    ProfileResponse
    Data Transfer Object (DTO) representing the profile information of a user.
    ProfileService
    Service layer responsible for handling user profile management operations such as viewing and updating user information, preferences, and account security.
    RecManager
    Service responsible for generating eatery recommendations based on user preferences, distance, dietary tags, and review metrics.
    RecommendationDto
    Data Transfer Object (DTO) representing an eatery recommendation.
    Review
    Entity representing a user-submitted review for an Eatery in the HealthyAura system.
    ReviewController
    Controller responsible for handling review-related operations for eateries.
    ReviewFlag
    Entity representing a user-submitted flag (report) on a specific Review.
    ReviewFlagRepository
    Repository interface for performing CRUD and custom query operations on ReviewFlag entities.
    ReviewFlagRequest
    Data Transfer Object (DTO) used when a user flags a review as inappropriate or misleading.
    ReviewRepository
    Repository interface for performing CRUD and custom query operations on Review entities.

    ReviewService
    Service layer responsible for managing user reviews, ratings, and moderation workflows.
    Reward
    Entity representing a redeemable reward in the HealthyAura reward system.
    RewardRepository
    Repository interface for performing CRUD and custom query operations on Reward entities.
    RewardResponse
    Data Transfer Object (DTO) representing the result of a successful reward redemption.
    RewardsController
    Controller responsible for managing user reward and points systems.
    RewardsService
    Service layer responsible for handling all reward- and points-related business logic in the HealthyAura ecosystem.
    SecurityConfig
    Central Spring Security configuration class that defines how authentication and authorization are handled throughout the HealthyAura backend.
    SignupRequest

    UpdateProfileRequest
    Data Transfer Object (DTO) used for updating a user's profile preferences.
    UpdateTagRequest
    Data Transfer Object (DTO) used for updating or renaming a tag associated with an eatery in the database.

    Users
    Entity representing a user account within the HealthyAura system.
    UserService
